ation\u003C/strong\u003E, and claim the crater.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also install Non-Comic Nuclear Physics so that I don\u0027t just grow random heads or anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-16T03:19:29Z\u0022 title=\u002202/16/2017 03:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 16, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by greenTurtle1134\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EInstall NCNP\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"munlander1","CreatedById":168560,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-16T03:23:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222956912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002210022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221487215071\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167701\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022greenTurtle1134\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, greenTurtle1134 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuitter\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003EHOW DARE YOU!!!!\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI storm into he crater and drop kick you out of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy freshly taken crater.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Raging Sandwich","CreatedById":164377,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-16T12:18:51Z","Conte